<sect1 id="dir_0c3bc48be24448a2d84a4b15107a07a4_1autotoc_md331">
<title>Transform Workflow</title><para>Each frame, transform state flows through the pipeline:</para>
<para>1. <bold>Input Systems</bold> write deltas to state components 2. <bold>ComposeTransformSystem</bold> combines deltas into final matrix 3. <bold>SceneSyncSystem</bold> copies matrix to SceneNode 4. <bold>TransformClearSystem</bold> resets dirty flags</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_0c3bc48be24448a2d84a4b15107a07a4_1autotoc_md332">
<title>Usage</title><para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Create<sp/>entity<sp/>with<sp/>transform<sp/>components<sp/>(via<sp/>builder)</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>entity<sp/>=<sp/>GameObjectFactory::gameObject()</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>.withTransform([](</highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal">&amp;<sp/>t)<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>t.transform()</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>.translate({0.0f,<sp/>0.0f,<sp/>0.0f})</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>.<ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1math_1ae230dbf0f416c8c868d5fea73d6babdb" kindref="member">scale</ref>({1.0f,<sp/>1.0f,<sp/>1.0f});</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>})</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>.make(</highlight><highlight class="keyword">true</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Direct<sp/>component<sp/>access<sp/>for<sp/>per-frame<sp/>updates</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal">*<sp/>translation<sp/>=<sp/>entity-&gt;get&lt;TranslationStateComponent&gt;();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">translation-&gt;add({1.0f,<sp/>0.0f,<sp/>0.0f});<sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Move<sp/>right</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal">*<sp/>rotation<sp/>=<sp/>entity-&gt;get&lt;RotationStateComponent&gt;();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">rotation-&gt;add(<ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1math_1a4949642a7cca09c7950bb6a1b75260c9" kindref="member">helios::math::radians</ref>(45.0f),<sp/><ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1math_1a64379fe55f1794fad912feafd5051224" kindref="member">helios::math::Z_AXISf</ref>);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Register<sp/>systems<sp/>in<sp/>correct<sp/>order</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">gameLoop.phase(PhaseType::Main).addPass()</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>.addSystem&lt;ComposeTransformSystem&gt;(&amp;gameWorld)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>.addSystem&lt;ScaleSystem&gt;(&amp;gameWorld);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">gameLoop.phase(PhaseType::Post).addPass()</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>.addSystem&lt;SceneSyncSystem&gt;(&amp;gameWorld,<sp/>&amp;scene)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>.addSystem&lt;TransformClearSystem&gt;(&amp;gameWorld);</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
